---
// No Ghost props — copy is entirely hard-coded for this section.
---

<section class="bg-[color:var(--color-fog)]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <p class="font-mono eyebrow text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
      Our Role
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug text-[color:var(--color-ink)] mb-4 max-w-xl">
      We Are Infrastructure. Not a Clinic.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">
      Revivum operates as the regulated backbone behind compliant peptide prescribing in Australia. We don&rsquo;t
      treat patients &mdash; we support the practitioners who do.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">📚</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Education</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          General health information for patients. Regulatory support for practitioners.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">🧭</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Navigation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Connecting curious patients with AHPRA-registered practitioners through a lawful pathway.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">🏭</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Supply</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          TGA-registered wholesale infrastructure. GMP-verified compounding supply for practitioners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
